  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE AN ENHANCED PENALTY FOR PERSONS SENTENCED AS HABITUAL MISDEMEANOR OFFENDERS; TO DEFINE TERMS; TO PROVIDE THAT IF A COURT FINDS THAT A DEFENDANT IS A HABITUAL MISDEMEANOR OFFENDER, THE DEFENDANT SHALL BE GUILTY OF A FELONY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
